  "datePublished": "2025-12-31",
  "description": "A tray is a shallow container used for growing [microgreens](./microgreen.md). In the context of microgreen cultivation, the tray holds the growing medium (typically a thin layer of soil, coconut coir, or hemp mat), retains moisture, and provides the surface area across which seeds are spread for even germination.",
